    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<h2 dir=\"ltr\">Long Hopper</h2>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Deviously intelligent, accepting a long hopper as a companion is much more a partnership than an ownership.</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Size </strong>Medium</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Type </strong>Fey</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Melee </strong><span class=\"pf2-icon\">A</span> bite (finesse), <strong>Damage </strong>1d6 piercing</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Str +0, Dex +3, Con +2, Int +0, Wis +1, Cha +0</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Hit Points </strong>8</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Skill </strong>Acrobatics</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Senses </strong>low-light vision</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Speed </strong>25 feet</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Support Benefit </strong>(auditory) With unheard squeaks far too high for most to hear, the long hopper guides its partner's motions, granting a +1 to attack rolls and damage rolls until the end of their turn.</p>\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\"><strong> </strong></h2>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Advanced Maneuver</strong>  Sudden Dash</p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\"><strong>Sudden Dash<span class=\"pf2-icon\">D</span></strong></p>\n<p dir=\"ltr\">Both the long hopper and its partner gain a +10 status bonus to their Speed for a minute. This cannot be used again for 20 minutes.</p>\n<h4 dir=\"ltr\">@UUID[Compendium.ponyfinder-bestiary-of-everglow.ponyfinder-bestiary-ancestries.Item.wCtY1gCeyPQvGHJC]{Sudden Dash}</h4>\n<h2 dir=\"ltr\"> </h2>",
